{"tid":1260434,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"關稅關稅～美國或將對越南加征關稅～","createTime":"2019-06-26T23:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T04:52:19.000Z","uid":252013,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c633d73a1676b2c9a1130810cfc8e89ad45482","tid":1260434,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T23:56:38.000Z","msg":"啲廠商啱啱先走，唔通又要再搬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n05:49 【美國或將對越南加征關稅】美國總統特朗普26日稱，越南占美國便宜比中國更甚。特朗普是當天在接受福克斯商業電視台採訪時說這番話的。當記者問是不是也要對越南加征關稅時，特朗普沒有否認，他說美國與越南正在就此進行討論。據美國貿易代表辦公室的統計數...<br />\n<br />\n來自秒聞 ‧ 實時財經急報app<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mutemute.com/share.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mutemute.com%2Fshare.php&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJT2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=1ba52859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mutemute.com/share.php</a>"},{"pid":"942ae1b7f711c617256b9fb0bbddcc60a48969be","tid":1260434,"uid":139916,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T23:58:30.000Z","msg":"集中追擊支好過啦"},{"pid":"2b8c2e368c81e6938a6e51065d0d8faf23222e1c","tid":1260434,"uid":997,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T23:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共和黨快手禁住佢"},{"pid":"54e54e967d2c3637f93457d80b520cdfad24b455","tid":1260434,"uid":146045,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:00:43.000Z","msg":"諗諗下只會循環<br />\n所有廠搬去越南<br />\n又到越南對美有大額貿易順差<br />\n之後美又加越南關稅<br />\n啲商家又要搬下個地方搬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c8deb6689f8d27cc617bed2c3545d1449a4281","tid":1260434,"uid":11724,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:02:41.000Z","msg":"係因為美國商經越南將中國貨入境避關稅所以先征"},{"pid":"c7bd93c8fbfb9719e5ef44b31